\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{y}_{i}(t):=\hat{R}(t)^{\top}\stackrel{o}{y}_{i}(t)$
\end_inset

并且
\begin_inset Formula $l_{i}>0,i=1,2$
\end_inset

。我们将这种组合预测器-观测器的性能与文献[4]中常增益观测器的一种ad-hoc方法进行了比较，以适应采样和延迟向量测量的情况。ad-hoc观测器的动力学为
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\hat{R}}_{\mathrm{ad}}(t)=\hat{R}_{\mathrm{ad}}(t)(\Omega(t)+\alpha(t))\times$
\end_inset

，其中
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{R}_{\mathrm{ad}}(t)$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $R(t)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha(t)$
\end_inset

是新息项。当姿态传感器在时间
\begin_inset Formula $t=t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}$
\end_inset

时刻提供测量样本
\begin_inset Formula $z_{1}\left(t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}\right)$
\end_inset

时，ad-hoc观测器的新息项受恒定增益观测器的启发，如
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha\left(t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}\right)=\bar{l}_{1}z_{1}\left(t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}\right)_{\times}\hat{R}_{\mathrm{ad}}\left(t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}-\tau_{1}\right)^{\top}\mathring{y}_{1}$
\end_inset

，其中
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{l}_{1}>0$
\end_inset

。该新息项将新接收的测量
\begin_inset Formula $z_{1}\left(t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}\right)$
\end_inset

与其估计
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{R}_{\mathrm{ad}}\left(t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}-\tau_{1}\right)^{\top}\mathring{y}_{1}$
\end_inset

进行比较，其中测量延迟的影响
\begin_inset Formula $\tau_{1}$
\end_inset

将被考虑
\begin_inset Foot
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
由于考虑了新息项中延迟的影响，可以将其视为Lyapunov-Krasovskii项[25]、[26]、[35]。
\end_layout

\end_inset

。类似地，在时间
\begin_inset Formula $t=t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}$
\end_inset

时刻，当测量
\begin_inset Formula $z_{2}\left(t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}\right)$
\end_inset

由姿态传感器传送时，新息项为
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha\left(t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}\right)=\bar{l}_{2}z_{2}\left(t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}\right)_{\times}\hat{R}_{\mathrm{ad}}\left(t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}-\tau_{2}\right)^{\top}\mathring{y}_{2}$
\end_inset

，其中
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{l}_{2}>0$
\end_inset

。如果某对
\begin_inset Formula $\left(k_{1},k_{2}\right)$
\end_inset

的
\begin_inset Formula $t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}$
\end_inset

恰好等于
\begin_inset Formula $t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}$
\end_inset

，那么新息项就是
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{l}_{1}z_{1}\left(t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}\right)_{\times}\hat{R}_{\mathrm{ad}}\left(t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}-\tau_{1}\right)^{\top}\mathring{y}_{1}+\bar{l}_{2}z_{2}\left(t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}\right)_{\times}\hat{R}_{\mathrm{ad}}\left(t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}-\tau_{2}\right)^{\top}\mathring{y}_{2}$
\end_inset

。对于没有任何向量测量样本的时间(即对于所有
\begin_inset Formula $t\notin\left(t_{k_{1}}\right)_{k_{i}=1}^{\infty}\cup\left(t_{k_{2}}\right)_{k_{i}=1}^{\infty}$
\end_inset

)，新息项为零，将观测器简化为姿态运动学的正积分。这个新息项的数学公式如下
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\alpha(t)=\begin{cases}
\bar{l}_{1}z_{1}\left(t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}\right)\times\hat{R}_{\mathrm{ad}}\left(t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}-\tau_{1}\right)^{\top}\mathring{y}_{1}, & t=t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}\neq t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}\\
\bar{l}_{2}z_{2}\left(t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}\right)\times\hat{R}_{\mathrm{ad}}\left(t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}-\tau_{2}\right)^{\top}\mathring{y}_{2}, & t=t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}\neq t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}\\
\sum_{i=1}^{2}\bar{l}_{i}z_{i}\left(t_{k_{i}}^{\prime}\right)\times R_{\mathrm{ad}}\left(t_{k_{i}}^{\prime}-\tau_{i}\right)^{\top}\mathring{y}_{i}, & t=t_{k_{1}}^{\prime}=t_{k_{2}}^{\prime}\\
0 & t\neq t_{k_{i}}^{\prime}
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset


